BlueServer - Connect with android phones from PC and send sms

In the two folders there are Eclipse projects for the server application that runs on PC
and the client application tha runs on Android phones.


- At first, run the server application and click the run server button on the GUI.
- After that, you run the Android app and scan for devices. Select the appropiate device.
- In server application fill in a phone number in the textbox and write some text in the textarea.
- Then click the send button.

You will see the text you have entered in the Pc on the phone's screen,
and an sms with this text is beeing sent to the number that you gave.